                    <h4>Age Group</h4>
            <ul>
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712165112/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Middle%20Age%20%2845%20to%2064%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Middle%2BAge%2B%2845%2Bto%2B64%2Byears%29">Middle Age (45 to 64 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712165112/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Adult%20%2819%20to%2044%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Adult%2B%2819%2Bto%2B44%2Byears%29">Adult (19 to 44 years)</a></li>                      
                        <li><a href="/web/20180712165112/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_Age_of_Target_Population=Adolescent%20%2813%20to%2018%20years%29&amp;fLockTerm=Adolescent%2B%2813%2Bto%2B18%2Byears%29">Adolescent (13 to 18 years)</a></li>                      
            </ul>
                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180712165112/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
